# Implementation Plan - AI Smart Job & Resume System

This project aims to build an end-to-end job seeker assistant that parses resumes, scores them for ATS compatibility, suggests improvements using a local LLM, and matches candidates with live job postings from India using RAG.

## Proposed Changes

### Project Structure
- `app.py`: Main Streamlit application.
- `src/`:
    - `parser.py`: Resume parsing logic (spaCy, Regex).
    - `llm.py`: Ollama integration for resume feedback and role detection.
    - `job_service.py`: Adzuna India API client and fraud filtering.
    - `rag_matcher.py`: FAISS and Sentence-Transformers for semantic matching.
    - `database.py`: SQLite storage for user history and notifications.
    - `notifier.py`: SMTP and APScheduler for email alerts.
- `requirements.txt`: Python dependencies.
- `.env`: API keys and configuration.

