## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test cases for resume parsing with sample documents.
- Mock API responses for Adzuna service.
- Similarity threshold verification for RAG.

### Manual Verification
- Uploading various resume formats (PDF, DOCX).
- Checking LLM-generated feedback for relevance.
- Verifying email notifications.
